data.description: This delightful Ranch home with finished basement has been wonderfully updated and lovingly maintained. Just minutes from shopping, restaurants and highway access! Front entry opens into light filled living room with new flooring and paint throughout. Large dining area opens into kitchen with lots of counter space and cabinetry. Two bedrooms on first floor share fully renovated full bath with large walk-in shower, new tile, lighting and cabinetry. Finished lower level with full bath is perfect additional space for office, den or kids room. Fully fenced backyard and mudroom added for convenience! Large two car garage with new roof. Updates include new Asphalt Roof (2023), Furnace (2023), A/C (2021), Hot Water Tank (2023), Range (2022) and more! Schedule a showing for this exceptional home today!
